episodes.title: Cult leaders FAIL at damage control after DISASTER expose 🔥
episodes.description:
Twin Flames Universe cult leaders Jeff and Shaleia Divine are reeling from a knockout interview where Jeff broke down and cried. In the wake of that disaster, they've gone back to their roots: rambling about nothing... and also how much they hate the media.

9:38 Rebooting their YouTube channel

episodes.title: Twin Flames Jeff Divine ACTUALLY thinks he's Jesus 🤣

In case you were wondering if Jeff Ayan (aka "Jeff Divine") believes himself to be Jesus, here it is in his own words. Jeff is the co-leader of Twin Flames Universe (TFU) which has been widely accused of being a cult, and is the subject of the Netflix series "Escaping Twin Flames".
